    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226460/extras/9d9b37be1384de8495408ed26bbe0576.poster.avif?t=1764610059\" width=736 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226460/extras/9d9b37be1384de8495408ed26bbe0576.webm?t=1764610059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226460/extras/9d9b37be1384de8495408ed26bbe0576.mp4?t=1764610059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226460/extras/dce4c47a4c02d57651ca4939177a35d5.poster.avif?t=1764610059\" width=608 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226460/extras/dce4c47a4c02d57651ca4939177a35d5.webm?t=1764610059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226460/extras/dce4c47a4c02d57651ca4939177a35d5.mp4?t=1764610059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226460/extras/6cbbcdd8f08ae04d1edffb3c9977a1ad.avif?t=1764610059\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226460/extras_big/6cbbcdd8f08ae04d1edffb3c9977a1ad.avif?t=1764610059 width=800 height=152 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this exciting and immersive game, players take on the role of a budding monster trainer as they explore a vast and fantastical world filled with all sorts of strange and wonderful creatures. With their trusty Montams in the team, players must journey across fields, forests, and caves in search of rare and powerful monsters to capture and train.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As players progress through the game, they will encounter an array of colorful and unique monsters, each with their own distinct abilities and personalities. Players must use strategy and skill to capture these monsters, and then use their training techniques to battle against rival trainers and emerge victorious.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226460/extras/c192cfdeea4f117e373118000e40f65c.poster.avif?t=1764610059\" width=608 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226460/extras/c192cfdeea4f117e373118000e40f65c.webm?t=1764610059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226460/extras/c192cfdeea4f117e373118000e40f65c.mp4?t=1764610059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226460/extras/96eedb01e09538825dc3a0d1f4f75b45.avif?t=1764610059\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226460/extras_big/96eedb01e09538825dc3a0d1f4f75b45.avif?t=1764610059 width=800 height=181 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, players can choose between three different battle systems: a classic turn-based system, a grid-based turn-based system or an active-battle system. All three systems offer unique challenges and gameplay experiences, allowing players to choose the style of battle that best suits their preferences and tactics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226460/extras/6a745ac0a56b40f6ffd753638488fd4c.poster.avif?t=1764610059\" width=608 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226460/extras/6a745ac0a56b40f6ffd753638488fd4c.webm?t=1764610059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226460/extras/6a745ac0a56b40f6ffd753638488fd4c.mp4?t=1764610059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226460/extras/67fb49d0135d475196d98549cb0ab8ca.avif?t=1764610059\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226460/extras_big/67fb49d0135d475196d98549cb0ab8ca.avif?t=1764610059 width=800 height=181 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition to the main game, every purchase of MonTamer also includes the MonTamer editor, a powerful tool that allows you to create your own monster-catching game without any programming experience. The editor includes event, mon, quest, item, ability, and dialog editors, as well as many other features that will help you bring your vision to life.<br> <br>To use the MonTamer editor, you will need to have the Unity game engine installed on your computer. Unity3D is a widely-used game engine that is available for free download, and it provides a powerful set of tools and resources that can be used to build games of all types. With the MonTamer editor and Unity3D, you'll have everything you need to create a unique and engaging monster-catching game that will keep players coming back for more. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226460/extras/4b1ce277f19e6e81126fc99ca4c04c6a.avif?t=1764610059\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226460/extras_big/4b1ce277f19e6e81126fc99ca4c04c6a.avif?t=1764610059 width=800 height=181 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep up with the latest developments in MonTamer by subscribing to our YouTube channel and joining our Discord server. We regularly post DevLogs to show you how the game is coming along and give you a behind-the-scenes look at the development process. Don't miss out on all the fun - start your journey as a MonTamer with us!</p>",
